Additions in this repository
----------------------------
* tec2_cli.cpp        — a curses-free, scriptable command-line simulator with
                        a persistent `--server` line protocol, and three custom
                        course-design instructions (MADD, MMOV, JNE).
* mcp/                — a Model Context Protocol server exposing the simulator
                        to AI tools, plus the custom-instruction microcode.
* headless_curses/    — a stub curses.h to build the original monitor headless
                        for output-for-output comparison.

